import React from "react";
import { Box, FormControl, InputLabel, Input, FormHelperText, TextField } from '@mui/material';

const ContactForm = () => {
    return(
        <Container maxWidth="xs">
        <Box
          sx={{
            mt: 20,
            display: "flex",
            flexDirection: "column",
            alignItems: "center",
          }}
        >
        <FormControl>
            <TextField
            helperText="Please enter your name"
            id="demo-helper-text-aligned"
            label="First Name"
            />
            <TextField
            helperText=" "
            id="demo-helper-text-aligned-no-helper"
            label="Last Name"
            />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
            <InputLabel htmlFor="my-input">Email address</InputLabel>
            <Input id="my-input" aria-describedby="my-helper-text" />
            <FormHelperText id="my-helper-text">example@example.com</FormHelperText>
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
            <TextField
            id="filled-textarea"
            label="Message"
            placeholder="message"
            multiline
            variant="filled"
            />
        </FormControl>
        </Box>
        </Container>
    );
}

export default ContactForm;
